<blockquote>
  <font size="3">`imshow` should be followed by `waitKey` function which displays the image for specified milliseconds. **Otherwise, it wonâ€™t display the image**. For example, `waitKey(0)` will display the window infinitely until any keypress (it is suitable for image display). waitKey(25) will display a frame for 25 ms, after which display will be automatically closed. (If you put it in a loop to read videos, it will display the video frame-by-frame)</font>
</blockquote>

